## Resource Categories

### Infrastructure

| Resource | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `qovery_organization` | Manages a Qovery organization |
| `qovery_cluster` | Manages Kubernetes clusters (AWS EKS, GCP GKE, Scaleway Kapsule) |
| `qovery_aws_credentials` | Manages AWS credentials for cluster provisioning |
| `qovery_gcp_credentials` | Manages GCP credentials for cluster provisioning |
| `qovery_scaleway_credentials` | Manages Scaleway credentials for cluster provisioning |

### Projects & Environments

| Resource | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `qovery_project` | Manages projects within an organization |
| `qovery_environment` | Manages environments within a project |

### Services

| Resource | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `qovery_application` | Manages applications built from git repositories |
| `qovery_container` | Manages containers deployed from container images |
| `qovery_job` | Manages jobs (cron or lifecycle) |
| `qovery_helm` | Manages Helm chart deployments |
| `qovery_terraform_service` | Manages Terraform service deployments |
| `qovery_database` | Manages databases |

### Configuration

| Resource | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `qovery_container_registry` | Manages container registry connections |
| `qovery_helm_repository` | Manages Helm repository connections (HTTPS and OCI) |
| `qovery_git_token` | Manages git provider tokens |
| `qovery_labels_group` | Manages reusable Kubernetes label groups |
| `qovery_annotations_group` | Manages reusable Kubernetes annotation groups |
| `qovery_deployment_stage` | Manages deployment stages for service ordering |
| `qovery_deployment` | Triggers deployments for an environment |

